import {Container,Row,Col,Form,Button} from 'react-bootstrap';

function SignupScreen(){
  return(
    <Container>
    <Row xs={12} md={7} className="justify-content-center align-items-center">
      <Col>
         <Form className="container my-2" expand="lg">
           <Form.Group>
             <Form.Label htmlFor="Fullname">Fullname:</Form.Label>
             <Form.Control type="text" name="Fullname" placeholder='Full Name'/>

             <Form.Label htmlFor="email">Email Adress:</Form.Label>
             <Form.Control type="email" name="Email" placeholder='Enter Email'/>


             <Form.Label htmlFor="password">Password:</Form.Label>
             <Form.Control type="password" name='password' placeholder='Password'/>

             <Form.Label htmlFor="AgainPassword">Again Password:</Form.Label>
             <Form.Control type="password" name='Again Password' placeholder='Again Password'/>

             <Form.Control type="phone" name='Again Password' placeholder='Again Password'/>

             <Form.Group className='d-grid'>
                <Button type='submit' size="lg" className='my-2 text-center' variant="success" expand="lg">Send</Button>
             </Form.Group>
           </Form.Group>
         </Form>
      </Col>
    </Row>
  </Container>
  )
}

export default SignupScreen;
